        <p style="color: white; font-size: 1.2rem; opacity: 0.9;">
            Modern User Management System with Real-time Analytics
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4">
            <a href="/showuser" class="btn-gradient" style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px; text-decoration: none;">
                <i class="fas fa-users"></i> View Users
            </a>
            <a href="/adduser" class="btn-gradient-outline" style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px; text-decoration: none;">
                <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Add New User
